---
---

<section id="privacy">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label fade-in">PRIVACY ARCHITECTURE</p>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in">AI Never Sees Real Names, Dates, or Identifying Information</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle fade-in">
      The anonymization boundary between Petra and Gavel ensures that real personally identifiable information is never processed by AI analysis agents. Only anonymized tokens are analyzed.
    </p>

    <div class="privacy-diagram fade-in">
      <div class="privacy-diagram__row">
        <div class="privacy-diagram__zone privacy-diagram__zone--local">
          <span class="privacy-diagram__zone-label">On-Premises (Document Intake)</span>
          <div class="privacy-diagram__agents">
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent">Lex</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent privacy-diagram__agent--highlight">Petra</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-diagram__boundary">
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-icon">&#x1F512;</span>
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-text">Anonymize</span>
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-sub">John Smith &rarr; PARTY_A<br/>2024-03-15 &rarr; DATE_A</span>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-diagram__zone privacy-diagram__zone--cloud">
          <span class="privacy-diagram__zone-label">AI Analysis (Anonymized Only)</span>
          <div class="privacy-diagram__agents">
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent privacy-diagram__agent--cloud">Gavel</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent privacy-diagram__agent--cloud">Reese</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent privacy-diagram__agent--cloud">Portia</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-diagram__boundary">
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-icon">&#x1F513;</span>
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-text">De-anonymize</span>
          <span class="privacy-diagram__boundary-sub">PARTY_A &rarr; John Smith<br/>Mapping purged</span>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-diagram__zone privacy-diagram__zone--local">
          <span class="privacy-diagram__zone-label">On-Premises (Delivery)</span>
          <div class="privacy-diagram__agents">
            <span class="privacy-diagram__agent">Sterling</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--3 stagger">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="card__title">Ephemeral Mappings</h3>
        <p class="card__description">Anonymization mappings exist only in memory during processing. They are never written to disk and are purged immediately after report delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="card__title">Local-First Processing</h3>
        <p class="card__description">Lex and Petra run entirely on your hardware with full PII access. Gavel, Reese, and Portia analyze only anonymized data. Sterling de-anonymizes locally.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="card__title">Audit Trail</h3>
        <p class="card__description">Every step is logged with timestamps. The audit records that anonymization was applied, without storing the actual mapping between real and anonymized values.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .privacy-diagram {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-3xl);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    min-width: 800px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__zone {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__zone--local {
    border-color: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.3);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__zone--cloud {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__zone-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__agents {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__agent {
    background: var(--color-surface-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__agent--highlight {
    border-color: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.5);
    color: #fb923c;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__agent--cloud {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.5);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__arrow {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .privacy-diagram__boundary {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.05);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    min-width: 140px;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__boundary-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__boundary-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .privacy-diagram__boundary-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-diagram__row {
      flex-direction: column;
      min-width: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
